<p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Only <code>focus-delegation</code> (now with <code>controller</code>), <code>selection</code>, and <code>anchor</code> are built today; <code>filter</code>, <code>clearable</code>, <code>live-status</code>, and <code>windowed</code> are spec-<strong>proposed</strong> trait surfaces. This page defines them as contracts — exactly as the family already does for <code>anchor</code>'s positioning strategy — not as shipped implementations.</p>

<h3>Altitude 1 — HTML, explicit behaviors (the substrate)</h3>
<p>Two elements, split by role: an <code>&lt;input role="combobox"&gt;</code> that owns the text and the query, and a <code>&lt;ul role="listbox"&gt;</code> that owns the collection and the active item. The input's <code>aria-activedescendant</code> points <em>into</em> the listbox; the listbox's <code>focus-delegation</code> declares the input as its <code>controller</code>. The JSX mirror is near-identity — only the inline comments (<code>&lt;!-- --&gt;</code> → <code>{/* */}</code>) and the two-root wrapper (a <code>&lt;&gt;</code> fragment) differ:</p>
{{ sourceToggle("autocomplete-substrate") }}
{% highlight "html" %}
<!-- INPUT-SIDE: owns DOM focus, the text, and the query -->
<input id="city-input" role="combobox"
       aria-controls="city-list"
       aria-autocomplete="list"
       aria-expanded="false"
       anchor="city-list"
       filter="async"                          <!-- STRUCTURAL: replaces type-ahead -->
       clearable>                              <!-- the "Clear" affordance -->

<!-- LISTBOX-SIDE: owns the collection and the active item -->
<ul id="city-list" role="listbox"
    focus-delegation="strategy=virtual;controller=city-input"   <!-- host is the input -->
    selection="model=single;selectionFollowsFocus=false"        <!-- STRUCTURAL: always local -->
    anchored="placement=bottom-start;collision=flip,resize"
    live-status                                <!-- "{n} results", "No results found" -->
    windowed                                   <!-- optional: virtualize large result sets -->
    popover>
  <!-- options are injected by `filter`, not authored -->
</ul>
{% endhighlight %}
{{ jsxSource("autocomplete-substrate") }}
{% highlight "tsx" %}
